            <p>To monitor the noise levels, we need access to your device&#8217;s microphone. No audio is recorded or sent to a server.</p>
            <button id="vnl-btn-activate" class="vnl-btn-primary">Start Monitoring</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- View: Active Monitor -->
    <div id="vnl-view-monitor" class="vnl-view">
        
        <!-- The Visualizer -->
        <div class="vnl-stage">
            
